|---|---------|-------|----------|-----|
| 1 | No security headers | A05 | 🔴 High | Add `helmet` |
| 2 | No rate limiting | A04 | 🔴 High | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| 3 | No authentication on `/users` | A01 | 🔴 High | Add auth middleware |
| 4 | No body parser size limits | A04 | 🔴 High | Set `limit` on body parsers |
| 5 | PII over-exposure in `/users` | A01/A03 | 🟠 Medium | Return minimal fields |
| 6 | No CORS policy | A05 | 🟠 Medium | Configure `cors` with allowlist |
| 7 | No input validation framework | A03 | 🟠 Medium | Add `express-validator` |
| 8 | No global error handler | A09 | 🟠 Medium | Add error middleware |
| 9 | Hardcoded port | A05 | 🟡 Low | Use `process.env.PORT` |
| 10 | Server fingerprinting | A05 | 🟡 Low | `app.disable('x-powered-by')` |
| 11 | No request logging | A09 | 🟡 Low | Add `morgan` |

